high_descs: Turn around and walk to the sink on the right.
Pick up the potato behind the egg in the sink on the right side.
Turn around and walk to the stove on the right.
Put the potato inside the microwave, heat it, remove it and close the door.
Turn around and walk to the sink on the left.
Put the heated potato in the sink to the left of the egg.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated potato in a sink.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the sink on your right
Pick up the potato that is sitting in the sink behind the egg
Turn around and walk to the stove on your right
Open the microwave that is above the stove and place the potato inside to the right of the tomato then close it and turn it on. Then open the microwave and pick up the potato and close the door
Turn to the right and go to the sink
Place the potato in the sink to the left of the egg
anns.task_desc: Place a cooked potato in a sink

high_descs: Turn around and face the sink on the right.
Pick up the potato from inside the sink.
Carry the potato and turn around, face the stove on the right side. Look up the microwave.
Open the microwave and place the potato inside. Shut the door and then open the door. Take out the potato and shut the door.
Carry the potato and turn to the right and move to the sink.
Place the cooked potato in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Heat a potato and place it in the sink.
